    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "（いつになったら{user}は）\n（戻ってくんだよ！　すぐ戻るって言ってたじゃん！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Just when is {user} coming back?!）\n（They said they'd be back in a second!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 6.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "（遅いわね……私達をこの状態で置き去りにしたまま）\n（もう十分は経ったわよ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（They're late… Leaving us stranded in this state‚）\n（it's already been ten minutes…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 14.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "（莉央もさー、なんで無言でこっち見てくんの……？）\n（はぁ……あと五分経って戻って来なければ帰ろっと）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（And what's up with Rio—why is she staring at me in silence…?）\n（Sigh… if they aren't back in five minutes‚ I'm going home.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 24.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "（こういう時って何か話した方がいいの……かしら？）\n（でも無言で十分も経ったのに今更話しかけるのも……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Should I say something in a moment like this…?）\n（But we've been silent for ten minutes; it's a bit late for small talk now…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 35.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "（あぁっ……気まずいっ……！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ugh… This is so awkward…!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 37.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "（あら……？　kanaの服……よく見たら……）\n（首元に何か紙？　みたいなものが付いてるわ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Wait…? kana's clothes… if I look closely…）\n（Is that a piece of paper stuck to her collar? It looks like a tag.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 46.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "（なになに、えっと……『シロサイクリーニング』）\n（着替える時に気が付きそうなものなのに）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Let's see‚ it says… \"White Rhino Dry Cleaners.\"）\n（You'd think she would've noticed when changing.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "（しっかりしているように見えて意外と）\n（おっちょこちょいなところがあるのね。ふふふっ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She seems so composed‚ but she's surprisingly）\n（clumsy in places like this. Hehehe…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 63.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "（な、なんなのよ、莉央……突然笑いかけてきて）\n（普通にキモいんだけど！　……あと四分）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Wh-What's with Rio… suddenly smiling at me?）\n（It's actually kind of creepy! …Four minutes left.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 71.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "（あっ、睨まれてしまったわ。でも、そうよね）\n（突然顔を見て笑われたら、気分を害して当然だわ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ah‚ she glared at me. Well‚ it's only natural.）\n（If someone suddenly looked at you and laughed‚ you'd be offended.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 81.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "（笑っちゃダメよ、神崎莉央！　でも、ダメって思えば）\n（思うほど面白く……ダメダメ！　くっ……ふふふっ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Don't laugh‚ Rio Kanzaki! But the more I tell myself not to‚）\n（the funnier it gets… No‚ no! Ugh… pfft‚ hehehe!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 90.4
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 94.1333374023
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "（なんで莉央は笑いながら自分の腕をつねってるの！？）\n（怖いんだけど、怖いんだけど！　……あと三分ね）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Why is Rio laughing while pinching her own arm?!）\n（This is scary‚ it's really scary! …Three minutes left.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.1333374023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 103.300004069
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "（ふー、落ち着くのよ、神崎莉央。一度目を閉じて……）\n（こういう時は、悲しいことを考えるの）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Phew‚ calm down‚ Rio Kanzaki. Close your eyes for a moment…）\n（In times like this‚ think of something sad.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.300004069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 114.1666707356
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "（悲しいこと……悲しいことと言えば……はっ！）\n（もしかしてkana、一日中あのタグをつけたまま？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Something sad… speaking of something sad… Wait!）\n（Has kana been wearing that tag all day long?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.1666707356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "（朝から晩まで誰からも指摘してもらえず……？）\n（『シロサイクリーニング』のタグをつけていたの？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Did nobody point it out to her from morning till night…?）\n（Did she go through the whole day with that \"White Rhino\" tag?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.9666707356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 131.2666707356
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "（はぁ……悲しいわね……franさんかmihoさんが）\n（教えてあげれば……いや、あの二人は指摘しなそうね）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Oh… how tragic… If only fran-san or miho-san）\n（had told her… No‚ those two wouldn't bother pointing it out.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.2666707356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 141.8333374023
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "（今度は何！？　なんでkanaの顔を見ながら）\n（涙浮かべてんのよ！？　疲れ過ぎだろ。あと一分……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Now what?! Why is she looking at my face）\n（with tears in her eyes?! She's lost it from exhaustion. One minute left…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.8333374023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 150.5333374023
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "（ふぅ、ここは私が教えてあげないと！　このままだと）\n（ずっとkanaにシロサイがついたままだわ！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Phew‚ I have to be the one to tell her! If I don't‚）\n（the \"White Rhino\" will stay on kana forever!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.5333374023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 159.6333374023
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_05-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "kana……！　シロサイが――",
